data.description: Looking for your forever home? This charming 1960s home with a brick and stone exterior sits on an UNRESTRICTED, 1 AC Lot at the end of the country lane! Imagine watching the seasons change through the large, mature tree-perfect for a tire swing, in your front yard. With plenty of space to garden or raise those backyard chickens for your farm fresh eggs each morning, you will love the location and the peace and quiet. Many updates have already been made to the over 2000 sq ft home including crank out replacement windows, and a tankless water heater. The detached 2 car garage boasts additional space for car and hobby storage. It has a separate bathroom installed, and a separate electrical entrance devoted to the garage.  The amount of space this home has to offer is deceiving from the exterior, don't wait, schedule your showing today!
